  <CantripDamage />
  <Name>On/Off</Name>
  <CastingTime>1 action</CastingTime>
  <Range>60 feet</Range>
  <Duration>Instantaneous</Duration>
  <Level>0</Level>
  <Description>This cantrip allows you to activate or deactivate any electronic device within range, as long as the device has a clearly defined on or off function that can be easily accessed from the outside of the device. Any device that requires a software based shutdown sequence to activate or deactivate cannot be affected by on/off.</Description>
